KNOWN ISSUES
=====================
- In case of cinnamon-control-center failed on NMDevice, reinstall
  Network-Manager and rebuild
- In case of muffin failed on SnMonitorContext, reinstall startup-notification
  and rebuild
- If KDE apps do not work on Cinnamon, try reinstalling qt
- Launching terminal from nemo shortcut did not work since they are not yet defined.
  Use this command to set it to other terminal (eg. xfce4-terminal)
  Thanks to Michael Amadio
  gsettings set org.cinnamon.desktop.default-applications.terminal exec xfce4-terminal
